videos.description: Washington's Dominic Green was not expecting the pass and it ends up with Prince Ali who flushes the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Ali flushes dunk off the sloppy turnover

videos.description: With the first half winding down, Jaylen Nowell knocks down a 3-pointer to extend Washington's lead.
videos.headline: Nowell drains the 3 at the end of the half

videos.description: UCLA's Cody Riley misses the dunk then gets a technical for hanging on the rim trying to put the ball back in.
videos.headline: Riley misses dunk then picks up the T
